description: Procedure information for the professional fees in the price estimate. Professional fees are generated in Resolute Professional Billing.

columns.name: ESTIMATE_ID
columns.description: The unique identifier for the price estimate record.

columns.name: LINE
columns.description: The line number for the information associated with this record. Multiple pieces of information can be associated with this record.

columns.name: CONTEXT_LINE
columns.description: References the context information from the table PR_EST_PROFEE_CXT.  This information is used to provide more accurate pricing information.

columns.name: PROC_ID
columns.description: The procedure entered in the price estimate to be priced.

columns.name: MODIFIERS
columns.description: The procedure modifiers associated with the service specified in the price estimate.

columns.name: QUANTITY
columns.description: The expected quantity of this procedure.

columns.name: CHARGE_AMOUNT
columns.description: The expected charge amount for this procedure.  This may also be referred to as the billed amount.

columns.name: ALLOWED_AMT
columns.description: The expected allowed amount specified for this procedure.

columns.name: SELF_PAY_AMT
columns.description: The expected self-pay amount specified for this procedure.

columns.name: SYS_SELF_PAY_AMT
columns.description: The system calculated self-pay amount for the professional charge.

columns.name: PB_ACTUAL_DISCOUNT_AMT
columns.description: Discount amount for estimated service.

columns.name: PB_SYSTEM_DISCOUNT_AMT
columns.description: System-calculated discount amount for estimated service.

columns.name: SYS_CHARGE_AMOUNT
columns.description: The system-calculated price for the associated professional charge.

columns.name: SYS_ALLOWED_AMT
columns.description: The system-calculated allowed amount for the associated professional charge.

columns.name: PB_DENTAL_RES_ID
columns.description: The dental procedure ID of the associated professional charge for an Estimate that originated from Epic's dental applicationï¿½treatment plan activity.

columns.name: PB_HX_CHGOVR_USR_ID
columns.description: The user who overrode the price of the associated professional charge on a Dental Estimate.

columns.name: PB_HX_ALLOVR_USR_ID
columns.description: The user who overrode the allowed amount of the associated professional charge for a Dental Estimate.

columns.name: PB_HX_SPOVR_USR_ID
columns.description: The user who overrode the self-pay amount of the associated professional charge for a Dental Estimate.

columns.name: PB_HX_CHGOVR_INST_DTTM
columns.description: The instant when the price of the associated professional charge was overridden for a Dental Estimate.

columns.name: PB_HX_ALLOVR_INST_DTTM
columns.description: The instant when the allowed amount of the associated professional charge was overridden for a Dental Estimate.

columns.name: PB_HX_SPOVR_INST_DTTM
columns.description: The instant when the self-pay amount of the associated professional charge was overridden for a Dental Estimate.

columns.name: PB_HX_CHGADJ_C_NAME
columns.description:
The reason the price of the associated professional charge was adjusted for a Dental Estimate.


May contain organization-specific values: Yes


 Category Entries: 


Overridden from Enterprise Billing

columns.name: PB_HX_ALLADJ_C_NAME
columns.description:
The reason the allowed amount of the associated professional charge was adjusted for a Dental Estimate.


 The category values for this column were already listed for column: PB_HX_CHGADJ_C_NAME

columns.name: PB_HX_SPADJ_C_NAME
columns.description:
The reason the self-pay amount of the associated professional charge was adjusted for a Dental Estimate.


 The category values for this column were already listed for column: PB_HX_CHGADJ_C_NAME

columns.name: PB_HX_CHGADJ_CMNT
columns.description: The free text comment associated with the price adjustment reason of the associated professional charge for a Dental Estimate.

columns.name: PB_HX_ALLADJ_CMNT
columns.description: The free text comment associated with the allowed amount adjustment reason of the associated professional charge for a Dental Estimate.

columns.name: PB_HX_SPADJ_CMNT
columns.description: The free text comment associated with the self-pay amount adjustment reason of the associated professional charge for a Dental Estimate.

columns.name: PROC_SVC_TYPE_ID
